# Auto 90/90 Farm
This script can automatically farm all the 90/90 era1 and/or inf1 for you, as long as you are powerful enough to beat them.

Should support all resolution and any dynamic ui setting.

The script will go through all regions and difficulties and try starting the farm. Also show you which era1s/inf1s you have already get.

Note: This script doesn't use skills or do era disables/dividers for you. You would need other scripts to do this(e.g. the finite infinite script).

## Settings
Edit them in the `main` script.

- `mode`: What the script should do. Can be `era` to farm all era1, `inf` to farm all inf1, and `enf`(default) to farm all era1 first, then try to farm inf1.
- `max_attempts`: How many times the script should restart tower testing when killed. If you can't reach era1/inf1 in that many amount of attempts, it would leave and skip this region/difficulty. Default 50.
- `dynamic_ui`: Whether you are using the dynamic ui setting. Should be `on`(default) or `off`.
